quote.summary: Chanhigh Holdings Ltd is an investment holding company primarily engaged in the landscape construction, municipal works construction and building works. The Company operates four segments. The Landscaping Construction segment is mainly engaged in the municipal and private landscaping projects such as planting of trees, modifying the layout of land, carrying out foundation work for landscape construction, building and construction of parks and other projects. The Municipal Works Construction segment is mainly engaged in the municipal or local government works such as municipal road construction, water and lighting works and other works. The Building Works segment is mainly engaged in the construction of gas stations, auto repair shops, office building and other buildings. The Others segment is mainly engaged in the maintenance, heritage restoration services and undertaking renovation works and agency income for trading of materials.
